# Title: Custom File Open Handler Executes PowerShell
# Author: CD_R0M_
# Date: 2022-06-11
# Level: high
# Description: Detects the abuse of custom file open handler, executing powershell
# MITRE Tactic: Uncategorized
# Tags: attack.stealth, attack.t1202
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/registry/registry_set/registry_set_custom_file_open_handler_powershell_execution.yml

Details="*powershell*" Details="*-command*" TargetObject="*shell\\open\\command\\*"